<div id="main">

<h1>Modal</h1>
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>This patch adds an insert mode to surf. While in the insert mode the
hotkeys without a MODKEY cannot be used, which allows you to type into a
text area/field without clashing with the hotkeys.</p>
<p>This patch modifies both the <code>config.def.h</code> and <code>surf.c</code> and removes
MODKEY modifier from most of the hotkeys (e.g. 'MODKEY+j' is now just
'j'). If you modify the patch to only apply to <code>surf.c</code> you should at
least have two hotkeys with a function called <code>insert</code>:</p>
<pre><code>{ 0,                     GDK_KEY_i,      insert,     { .i = 1 } },
{ 0,                     GDK_KEY_Escape, insert,     { .i = 0 } },
</code></pre>
<p>Note that if the modifier is <code>0</code>, <code>GDK_KEY_Escape</code> is the only key that
you can use to get out of the insert mode.</p>
<h2>Download</h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="surf-modal-20190209-d068a38.diff">surf-modal-20190209-d068a38.diff</a></li>
